forest walk

A type of terrain walk. A creature that has forest walk ignores difficult terrain that is part of a tree, underbrush, or some other forest growth.

Published in Monster Manual 2, page(s) 217, Monster Manual, page(s) 281, Rules Compendium, page(s) 311, Monster Vault: Threats to the Nentir Vale, page(s) 123.
